    #include <iostream>
#include <vector>
#include <list>
#include <set>

int main()
{
	map<int, char> container;

	for (int i = 0; i < 10; ++i)
		container.insert(make_pair(i, char(i + 65)));

	vector<int>::const_iterator itr;
	
	for (auto& itr : container)
		cout << itr->first << "  " << itr->second << endl;
	cout << endl;
}
